Description: Bayesian estimates of trophic position leveraging 'brms' using 
             stable isotope data.Trophic position modeles are created using 
             equations from 
             Post (2002) <doi:10.1890/0012-9658(2002)083[0703:USITET]2.0.CO;2>, 
             and 
             Huevel et al. (2024) <doi:10.1139/cjfas-2024-0028>. 
